---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Technology Partners | Generalsoft UAE"
  description="Generalsoft partners with global technology leaders like Microsoft, Google, Apple, IBM, Cisco, and Oracle to deliver world-class software and IoT solutions in the UAE."
  path="/partners/"
>
  <main>
    <section class="page-header" style="padding: 100px 0 50px; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f, #fdbb2d); color: white;">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Strategic Partnerships</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">Collaborating with the world's most innovative technology companies to empower businesses in the UAE and beyond.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="partners-content" style="padding: 80px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="service-card">
            <h3 style="color: #2563eb;">Microsoft</h3>
            <p>Utilizing Azure Cloud ecosystems and enterprise software suites to build scalable, secure cloud-native applications for the modern workplace.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card">
            <h3 style="color: #4285F4;">Google</h3>
            <p>Leveraging Google Cloud Platform and cutting-edge TensorFlow frameworks to integrate advanced Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning into our solutions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card">
            <h3 style="color: #000;">Apple</h3>
            <p>Developing premium native iOS and macOS experiences, ensuring our mobile applications meet the highest standards of performance and design.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card">
            <h3 style="color: #0530ad;">IBM</h3>
            <p>Partnering for enterprise-grade infrastructure and specialized systems design, focusing on hybrid cloud and robust data management.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card">
            <h3 style="color: #1271bf;">Cisco</h3>
            <p>Integrating world-class networking and security hardware to provide our clients with reliable, high-performance network designs and IoT infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card">
            <h3 style="color: #f80000;">Oracle</h3>
            <p>Building data-intensive applications backed by Oracle's industry-leading database management systems and cloud ERP solutions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta" style="padding: 60px 0; background: #f8f9fa; text-align: center;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to build with the best?</h2>
        <p>Contact us today to discuss how our partnerships can benefit your next project.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 12px 30px; background: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Work With Us</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>